casebody.head_matter:
NEW HAMPSHIRE, petitioner,
v.
Michael SOTO, et al.
No. 14-639.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 7, 2016.
Motion of respondents Robert Dingman and Eduardo Lopez, Jr., for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of New Hampshire denied.
